    public abstract class SwCommunicationResourceImpl
extends SwInteractionResourceImpl
implements SwCommunicationResource
    An implementation of the model object 'Sw Communication Resource'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Speed Factor
    • Main Scheduler
    • Element Size
    • Base Connector
    • Transm Mode
    • Block T
    • Packet T
    • Capacity
